cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CL

The paper deals with video summarization, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). It also involves machine learning techniques for identifying important events and selecting representative views, which falls under the categories of multimedia (cs.MM) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of annotations and consensus analysis, which are common in information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
